olor: inherit;"><a href="latin-america.php">Doing Business in Latin America</a></span><br></li></ul></div></div><div class="hr"></div><div class="h2"><b>Our Approach</b></div><div id="i10">At Edward Professional Advisors, we use evidence-based practices to help our clients solve their problems. Evidence-based solutions draw on a variety of academic and business disciplines, including organizational improvement, positive organizational psychology, sociology, human development, and leadership. Because of the broad range of our collective experiences, we are able to offer our clients holistic solutions to their most challenging problems.</div><div id="i11"><div><ul><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">We focus on integrating best practice ideas and leading academic theories into real-world situations.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">We believe that success is never accidental; it always takes careful planning and deliberate execution to reach one’s goals.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">We practice a holistic-systems approach to problem-solving.</span><br></li></ul></div></div><div class="hr"></div><div class="h2"><b>Our Professional Affiliations</b></div><div id="i14"><div><ul><li><a href="http://www.amanet.org/new-homepage.aspx" target="_blank">American Management Association</a></li><li><a href="http://www.apa.org/" target="_blank">American Psychological Association</a></li><li><a href="http://www.isfcp.net/" target="_blank">International Society for Coaching Psychology</a></li><li><a href="http://www.siop.org/" target="_blank">Society for Industrial &amp; Organizational Psychology</a></li></ul></div></div><div class="next-page"><div id="i16"><a href="capabilities-statement.php"><u>Next: Capabilities Statement &gt;</u></a></div></div><div style="clear: both;"></div></div></div><div id="footer"><div id="i18">© 2016 - EDWARD PROFESSIONAL ADVISORS<div>i